{"tid":1628004,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【毅進制迷團】8月5日到底放咗幾多催淚彈？","createTime":"2019-10-05T20:21:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T17:35:34.000Z","uid":87553,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"43950e5f7db98b6e8d3a2f544c41ebf402c14629","tid":1628004,"uid":87553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T20:21:28.000Z","msg":"8月嗰陣，警察話8月5號放咗約<span style=\"color: gold;\">800</span>粒催淚彈、約<span style=\"color: gold;\">140</span>發橡膠子彈、約<span style=\"color: gold;\">20</span>發海棉彈。9月中經濟日報同警察查詢數字，收到回覆之後做報導都係寫呢個數，有post為證：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1578990\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1578990</a><br />\n<br />\n但係後來經濟日報改咗篇文，話當日用咗「逾千枚催淚彈」，詳細數字係<span style=\"color: gold;\">1002</span>粒催淚彈、<span style=\"color: gold;\">170</span>發橡膠子彈、<span style=\"color: gold;\">11</span>發布袋彈、<span style=\"color: gold;\">28</span>發海棉彈。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2454469/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2454469%2F&d=15TDSCYqMG0%2FxcOE0oxfEHWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=bcd33da6\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2454469/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解個數又可以好似6.12數字咁變？到底係警察報細數定係經濟日報數錯？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">到底8月5日用咗幾多火力對付人民？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重有冇其他真相未發掘？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"cc17e5343ea2e35964a3361f09356d324854ced2","tid":1628004,"uid":87553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T20:23:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce88955cf1f6ecf49f014d4ec9af64fe47c2316e","tid":1628004,"uid":87553,"like":0,"disli